Let’s unpack the science of vibrant-looking skin. ✨ 

NEW Even Better Clinical Vitamin Makeup is formulated with a brilliant combination of potent vitamins and SPF protection for skin that glows with healthy radiance. 

⚡ 4% vitamin B3 helps boost skin’s natural energy for vibrant, healthy-looking skin. 

✨ 5 forms of vitamin C are designed to penetrate at different rates, and provide multi-action benefits—2 forms help visibly brighten skin and 3 types help provide antioxidant protection.

💪 Vitamin E is a powerful antioxidant that helps provide antioxidant defense for the lipid barrier. 

🔆 Hybrid sunscreen system with a blend of chemical and physical sunscreens provides UVA/UVB protection, helping protect skin from future sun damage.
 
It’s also: 
👩‍⚕️ Dermatologist tested.
👍 Safe for sensitive skin.
🧪 Allergy tested.
🚫 Fragrance free.

You should know these skin barrier basics ⬇️
🔝 “Skin barrier” refers to the top layer of your skin. 
🙅‍♀️ Helps keep bad stuff (i.e. environmental stressors) out. 
👍 Helps keep good stuff (i.e. moisture) in. 
💪 Strong skin barrier = visibly happy and hydrated skin. 

And how can you strengthen your skin barrier, you might ask? 
That’s precisely what Dramatically Different Moisturizing Lotion+ is for.☝️
🧑‍🔬 Dermatologist developed. 
🧪 Allergy tested.
🚫 100% fragrance free.
